<h1>Persona</h1>
<br>

<h2>Statistics</h2>

<p class = header2>Name: </p> <p class = indent>Jonah Whalie</p><br>
<p class = header2>Gender: </p> <p class = indent>Male</p><br>
<p class = header2>Age: </p> <p class = indent>60</p><br>
<p class = header2>Profession: </p> <p class = indent>Indigent</p><br>
<p class = header2>Income: </p> <p class = indent>Disability</p><br>

<h2>Technology:</h2>

<p class="userStory">He has an older iPhone 6 and uses the public library computers</p>

<h2>Attitudes and Behaviors:</h2>

<p class="userStory">He needs access to multiple government provided
    services for his meds, counseling, and other services
    to help get himself back in a stable environment. He is really trying to straighten out his life </p>

<h2>Frustrations and Needs:</h2>

<p class="userStory">Having to live on the streets, he has to use his phone to connect with
    public transportation. He needs to know if a bus is on time and where it is
    so he can plan his routes to make his appointments.</p>

<h2>Goals:</h2>

<p class="userStory">He wants to take more control of his life and get it back on track.</p>

<h2>User Story:</h2>

<p class="userStory">It's a hard life living on the streets, and I am want to get better and be able to
    see my family again.</p>

